The recommendations precipitating from the 2024 PHA Revalidation are summarized in the associated report.  All recommendations are documented, with a date of a completion and description of the action required.  The human factors were discussed in the 2024 PHA Revalidation as a separate node.  The worksheets can be found in the PHA Revalidation report, which also include; major hazards identified, process controls in use, mitigation systems in use, and monitoring and detection systems in use.
